{"_id":"Rdut9K447vZuLo2A","name":"Eldritch Automata — Panic","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","description":"Roll D6 + Stress Level when a bane appears on a Stress Die.","formula":"1d6","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"EwOXovQcWTEXGYHA","type":"text","text":"<strong>Stable.</strong> You are keeping it together.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":6,"range":[1,6],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"uCa1jlbeaMGB8qA8","type":"text","text":"<strong>Trembling.</strong> You start to tremble. Modification −1 to all rolls for Agility for the rest of the scene.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"3DvwFpGRYobpZ2X9","type":"text","text":"<strong>Anxious.</strong> <em>Stability</em> reduces by 1.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[8,8],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"7Vih9SgPyDseajI8","type":"text","text":"<strong>Sullen.</strong> <em>Ego</em> reduces by 1.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[9,9],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"NbckRAYw5bbrwVhh","type":"text","text":"<strong>Shaking.</strong> The fear is starting to get to you. The Stress Level of yourself and all of your friendly PCs in <em>Short</em> Range of you, increase by 1.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[10,10],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"4QxffHesbswyvQZY","type":"text","text":"<strong>Freeze Up.</strong> You tense up in fear, losing your next <em>Slow</em> Action. Your Stress Level and all other friendly PCs in <em>Short</em> Range of you, increase by 1.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[11,11],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"qhhRkWGXAK0MEUm3","type":"text","text":"<strong>Scream.</strong> You scream for 1 Round, losing your next <em>Slow</em> Action. Your Stress is reduced by 1, but every friendly character who hears your screams must roll for <strong>Panic</strong>.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[12,12],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"3B8JIbkWH1DvjJBe","type":"text","text":"<strong>Run Away.</strong> You can't do this anymore, you have to run. You must flee from danger until you are in what is deemed a safe place. Your <em>Stress</em> Level is decreased by 1 but all other friendly PCs roll <strong>Panic</strong>.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[13,13],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"t9Nob6XLvBOLCKGk","type":"text","text":"<strong>Hallucinations.</strong> You are suffering from powerful hallucinations and are unsure what is real or not. The GM determines the details. Reduce your <em>Stability</em> and <em>Ego</em> by 1.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[14,14],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"EI9nt7edX2gGiTxq","type":"text","text":"<strong>Berserk.</strong> You immediately enter your <em>Berserk</em> state if you're piloting an Automata. If you are not, you become Enraged, attacking the nearest thing near you until you are subdued. Reduce your <em>Stability</em> by 1.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[15,15],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"TxDZ2A8RfoGjdUpM","type":"text","text":"<strong>BSOD.</strong> Your mind needs to go away for a second. You stare off into space, not able to speak or move or take any action. Only by someone taking a <em>Slow</em> Action to physically shake and call out to you can you return. Reduce your <em>Stability</em> by 1.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":84,"range":[16,99],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}}],"flags":{}}
